E2AUD.original: ~z~You want to start rolling with me, drive me back to my crib in Northwood on X.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~你要是想跟我混，就送我回我在Northwood的Xenotime街的公寓。

E2AUD.original: ~z~Nah? You sound like you coming outta Russia with that accent. That all good, money.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~不是吗？听口音你像是俄罗斯出来的。也没事，老弟。

E2AUD.original: ~z~There ain't a deal in this town I don't know about. I own this city, for real.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~这座城市里就没有我不知道的交易。城市是我的，真的。

E2AUD.original: ~z~You take a bid on a heroin beef you ain't seeing light for a long time.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~一旦被卷入海洛因的交易，你就得过上好久暗无天日的生活了。

E2AUD.original: ~z~For real. My crib's over on Galveston Avenue in North Holland.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~是真的。我的宝贝家在North Holland的Galveston Avenue上。

E2AUD.original: ~z~Shit, I don't know, all type of shit.
~z~Why I surround myself with you people?
~z~For sure, reach for the stars and all that shit!
~z~I don't go near the stuff... professionally... but I found him a buyer.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~我不卖那玩意...说真的...但我帮他找了个买家。

E2AUD.original: ~z~Build me some skyscrapers. See my name in big gold letters.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~给我建一些摩天大楼，看着我的名字金光闪闪的刻在上边。

E2AUD.original: ~z~Elizabeta don't get me to do shit. I just like to keep an eye on things.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~不是Elizabeta叫我去做事。我只是想盯着情况。

E2AUD.original: ~z~We gonna hit up the roof. You clear out the floor above first, money.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~我们就冲上楼顶，你先把楼上给清了，老弟。

E2AUD.original: ~z~A heroin deal is your way of diversifying?
~z~What type of shit you got going on? I'm always looking for work, if it pays that is.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~你还在做什么生意？我一直都在找活，能赚钱就行。

E2AUD.original: ~z~We see what happens. I got some more deals to make.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~我们走着瞧。我还有更多交易要做。

E2AUD.original: ~z~Any of you friends on the inside?
~z~Get involved in some extreme shit. Change the game.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~被卷入一些极端烂事里。改变游戏格局。

E2AUD.original: ~z~I like to make money, but there should be other considerations when you go into business with a person.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~我喜欢赚钱，但你和别人做生意应该还有其他考量吧。

E2AUD.original: ~z~Should be like double X or triple X or something on that one though.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~其实应该是两个X或者三个X以上的尺码。

E2AUD.original: ~z~The amount of... what you call dollars in Russia?
E2AUD.translated: ~z~钱的数量...你们管俄罗斯的钱叫什么？

E2AUD.original: ~z~Yo. They gonna expect us to go out the front with that biker dude.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~哟，他们肯定以为我们会和摩托老哥一起走正门。

E2AUD.original: ~z~Now, Johnny is sitting on a big pile of heroin.
~z~My man Dwayne Forge is inside on a crack beef.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~我哥们Dwayne Forge就因为卖霹雳可卡因进去了。

E2AUD.original: ~z~I pay like a Shlongberg Sachs bonus, bitch.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~我给的钱跟隆盛集团的分红一样丰厚，贱人。

E2AUD.original: ~z~-I am the best, I am number one!~n~-Later.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~－我是最棒的，我是最强的！~n~－回见。

E2AUD.original: ~z~I have learnt that at a price.
~z~Playboy X don't like coming that close to being taken down.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~Playboy X可不喜欢命悬一线的感觉。

E2AUD.original: ~z~shit, I'm looking into expanding my horizons.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，调查以后我也是大开眼界。

E2AUD.original: ~z~I want to be spending rubles like you gangsters.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~我只想像你们俄国黑帮一样花卢布潇洒。

E2AUD.original: ~z~Playboy X? What's the X stand for?
~z~What's wrong with you? You're being fucking weird.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~你有什么毛病？你他妈的很怪。

E2AUD.original: ~z~It's like extra large as well. All type of bitches be calling me that, yeah.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~也代表XL的尺码。所有母狗都那么说我，没错。

E2AUD.original: ~z~The coast is cleared. Come on, Playboy.
~z~Elizabeta, your friend, the playboy, he's dead. The contact was a cop.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~Elizabeta，你的朋友，那个Playboy，他死了。联络人是个警察。

E2AUD.original: ~z~I ain't scared of nobody. All them bikers is racist as shit is all.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~我谁都不怕。飞车党都是搞种族歧视的傻逼。

E2AUD.original: ~z~This is a cash deal. I got other shit going down as well.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~都是钱的事儿。别的生意我也有做。

E2AUD.original: ~z~I'm buying and selling that shit like any commodity on the trading floor.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~我买卖那玩意儿跟在证交所买卖商品是一样的。

E2AUD.original: ~z~Yeah? You short of money at the moment?
~z~Playboy was a fool, but he earned. This ain't good. Come back to see me.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~Playboy是个傻子，但是他能挣钱。这可不好。快回来找我。

E2AUD.original: ~z~These ones won't be causing no trouble. We move.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~这些家伙不会再添乱了，我们走。

E2AUD.original: ~z~That was crazy, money. You a good man to have around when the shit goes down.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~这简直疯了，老弟。遇到这种鸟事时你能够在身边太好了。

E2AUD.original: ~z~Don't want to even look at him the wrong way, crazy motherfucker.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~没事都不敢看他一眼，狗逼疯子。

E2AUD.original: ~z~Well, I got to go pick up the stuff so, uh, I'll see you there.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~行，我先回去拿趟货，所以...到地方见。

E2AUD.original: ~z~Why I surround myself with you people?

E2AUD.translated: ~z~所以才要盯着这次的海洛因交易？

E2AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, but Playboy is going legitimate. I wanna be one of them developer cats.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~是的，但是Playboy要洗白自己。我也想做一个房产商。

E2AUD.original: ~z~Hey! Playboy! X! Ha ha! This is Niko.
~z~Street cats like me just get labeled as pimps, and pushers and stickup artists.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~像我这样的街头混混只会被贴上皮条客、毒贩子、抢劫艺术家的标签。

E2AUD.original: ~z~You ain't right, friend, come on... let's get out of here.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~你不对劲，朋友，好了...咱们快走吧。

E2AUD.original: ~z~I got rid of these guys. Let's go.
~z~Does Elizabeta get you to do stuff like this often?
~z~Pato! No money and a good earner is dead.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~够了！钱没赚到能赚钱的人又死了。

E2AUD.original: ~z~I ain't doing a bid for this shit. Stick to me, player.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~我可没为这鸟事投保，跟紧我，玩家。

E2AUD.original: ~z~I'm afraid that your friend Playboy, he had an accident, he ain't gonna be around no more.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~恐怕你的朋友Playboy他出事了，他不会再出现在你身边了。

E2AUD.original: ~z~Not big enough for some people. What that other gang called? Death Angels or some shit.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~对某些人还不够大。另一派叫啥来着？死灵天使还是啥的。

E2AUD.original: ~z~Hey... what's going on guys, what's going on?
E2AUD.translated: ~z~嘿...你们好吗，伙计，你们还好吗？

E2AUD.original: ~z~Shit man. I'd a fucking died instead of being caught by them feds.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，老弟。比起被FIB抓住，我宁愿直接去死。

E2AUD.original: ~z~You think I'm short of paper? I just helping out on this deal because Liz is my business partner.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~你觉得我会缺票子？我给这次交易帮忙，只是因为Liz是我的生意伙伴。

E2AUD.original: ~z~Why you not fucking keep hold of him?
~z~Hell yeah, the amount of rubles being dropped up in Liberty City is a joke.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~太对了，自由城的卢布数量逐渐下降就是个笑话。

E2AUD.original: ~z~We need to get out through the roof, player.
~z~Gimme them digits, we see if we can make shit happen.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~给我你的号码，说不定以后我们能干成些大事。

E2AUD.original: ~z~But you've got the heroin, correct? You're carrying it, correct? I mean it's a simple question.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~你们手头有海洛因，对吧？你们带过来了，对吧？就这么简单一问题。

E2AUD.original: ~z~Maybe I do got work for y'all.
~z~I never been to Russia, but I think their money is called rubles.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~我没去过俄罗斯，不过那里的钱好像叫卢布。

E2AUD.original: ~z~He showed me some shit back in the day but shit...
E2AUD.translated: ~z~当年他确实教了我不少玩意，不过...

E2AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, I thought you would want to build schools or something.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~是吗，我还以为你会想建一些学校之类的。

E2AUD.original: ~z~Surround yourself with cocaine and the assholes soon follow...
E2AUD.translated: ~z~坐拥大批可卡因，混蛋们就会靠过来...

E2AUD.original: ~z~I don't care about the exchange rate or nothing.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~我不在乎汇率那些有的没的。

E2AUD.original: ~z~He doing all type of crazy shit. Blowing stuff up.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~他做着各种各样疯狂的事，狂轰乱炸。

E2AUD.original: ~z~Not weird, man, I just wanna know if you're carrying the stuff right?
E2AUD.translated: ~z~不怪，老兄，我只是想知道你们是不是带了货？

E2AUD.original: ~z~Here we be, money. I'll hit you up when I need your ass.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~我们到了，老弟。需要你丫的时候我会找你的。

E2AUD.original: ~z~I want to get my hands on some of that shit.
~z~They be more of them FIB cats up in this shit.
~z~You obviously ain't been big time. I started small like you, player.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~你之前肯定还不够格。刚开始我也是小喽啰，玩家。

E2AUD.original: ~z~Yo, money. We going down through this sucker.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~哟，老弟，我们差点被那群混蛋搞掉。

E2AUD.original: ~z~For sure. Let me hook up with your number. You got a cell, right?
E2AUD.translated: ~z~当然，让我存一下你的手机号。你有手机，对吧？

E2AUD.original: ~z~Them boys, the Lost, they in some heavy type of gang war is what I heard. Crazy whiteboy shit.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~那群家伙，失落帮，好像在进行激烈的帮派战争。一群白皮疯子。

E2AUD.original: ~z~Shit, that'll come. Got to get me successful first.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~靠，以后会有的。先让我成功再说。

E2AUD.original: ~z~Johnny, your biker friend, got himself killed before the meet. Sorry.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~Johnny，你的摩托帮朋友，在见面交易前就死了。抱歉。

E2AUD.original: ~z~For real. That's how shit works up in here.
~z~Tell me about that biker, the one with the smack, Johnny.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~跟我讲讲那个飞车党吧，有海洛因的那个，Johnny。

E2AUD.original: ~z~I want as many people around this deal as possible.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~我想让尽量多的人盯着这次交易。

E2AUD.original: ~z~Uh, I'll catch up with you. How you doing?
E2AUD.translated: ~z~呃，待会儿再陪你跳。近况如何啊？

E2AUD.original: ~z~There be the smack tip, the rap game, X, chronic, meth...
E2AUD.translated: ~z~有海洛因针管，说唱游戏，摇头丸，大麻，冰毒...

E2AUD.original: ~z~Help young black men get out of the ghetto.
~z~A future in a max security pen ain't no future at all.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~在戒备最严的监牢里的未来根本不算是未来。

E2AUD.original: ~z~The deal didn't go so good. Charlie was an undercover cop.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~交易不太顺利。Charlie是个卧底警察。

E2AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, well how come we haven't met before?
E2AUD.translated: ~z~是吗，之前咱俩咋没遇上过呢？

E2AUD.original: ~z~Maybe I could use a boy like you on team Playboy.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~也许我们Playboy小队里可以用你这种家伙。

E2AUD.original: ~z~I ain't workin with that cat but I heard about him.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~我没跟那家伙合作过，但我听说过他。

E2AUD.original: ~z~She my SoBo connection, hooks me up when I need her to.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~她是我在South Bohan的线人，需要的时候她就会联系我。

E2AUD.original: ~z~That why I look after her when she need me to.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~所以只要她需要我，我就会帮她照顾下。

E2AUD.original: ~z~What's different since this guy's been doing his bid?
E2AUD.translated: ~z~自从他坐牢以后有什么变化？

E2AUD.original: ~z~Sure, let's do this. Nothing like selling some dope to let you know you're alive.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~当然，我们开干吧。只有贩毒才能让你有活着的感觉。

E2AUD.original: ~z~It's like X marks the spot. That's coz I was always on the same corner pushing weight.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~就像用X标记目标一样。因为我总是在同一处卖大麻。

E2AUD.original: ~z~I don't see it as dealing drugs. Drugs is just one arm of my business.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~我不认为这是贩毒。毒品只是我生意的冰山一角。

E2AUD.original: ~z~You forget about them cats that do that sort of time.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~一直蹲在里头的家伙会被遗忘。

E2AUD.original: ~z~Pop these dudes. They got to the party late.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~毙了他们，谁让他们派对迟到了。

E2AUD.original: ~z~So, who else do you need to meet, huh?
E2AUD.translated: ~z~那么，你还得跟谁认识认识，哈？

E2AUD.original: ~z~Get some pace on, player. We ghosting through here.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~步子大点，玩家。我们潜行出去。

E2AUD.original: ~z~Shit changed. There be more to it than the crack tip nowaday.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~都他妈变了。现在可不只是霹雳可卡因一种。

E2AUD.original: ~z~So, is you Russian or something? Is you like one of them oligarchs or some shit?
E2AUD.translated: ~z~你是俄罗斯人还是哪儿人？你是不是那种独裁者？

E2AUD.original: ~z~That just what I'm doing to get outta the ghetto.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~我那么做只是为了离开贫民区。

E2AUD.original: ~z~Them was the old days. Now it's all about diversification.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~都是陈年往事了。现在讲究多元化经营。

E2AUD.original: ~z~Always on the same spot so X.
~z~Playboy's in bed with Liz because she got the hookups.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~Playboy愿意跟Liz上床是因为她有渠道。

E2AUD.original: ~z~Not yet. I got to set shit up. But I'll need a cat like you real soon. Gimme your number.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~还没有。得去安排安排，但我之后会需要你这样的人的。给我你的电话。

E2AUD.original: ~z~Me and Liz are entrepreneurs. Shit, if the deal makes paper, I do it.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~Liz和我都是生意人。妈的，要是这生意能赚钱，我就去做。

E2AUD.original: ~z~I don't see why a young kid from the hood can't make something out of himself...
E2AUD.translated: ~z~我不觉得贫民窟出来的孩子没法自己做出一番事业...

E2AUD.original: ~z~Shit. The boy will say anything to get out of doing hard time.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~靠。那小子为了不蹲号子什么都会说的。

E2AUD.original: ~z~Elizabeta, things didn't go so good. The contact was...
~z~We going down to Cassidy Street in Schottler.
~z~Think only one group can grow beards and ride bikes in this town.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~都认为只有一派可以蓄着胡子在城里骑摩托。

E2AUD.original: ~z~Slinging rocks on the corner, sticking cats up, all type of shit.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~到街上卖药，拿枪顶着人，各种脏活。

E2AUD.original: ~z~Buyer is some Asian dude called Charlie.
~z~Russia's big right now. Rabbit fur hats, Cherenkov vodka, I love that shit.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~俄罗斯现在强大了。什么兔皮帽子，契连科夫伏特加，我超爱那些。

E2AUD.original: ~z~That's probably why you rolling with her too.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~这大概也是你跟她混的原因。

E2AUD.original: ~z~I ain't gonna use no fool's name, hell no. X is a fuck you to them fools who thought they owned me.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~我才不会用傻逼名字，绝不会。对那些自以为掌控我的傻子来说X就是X你妈。

E2AUD.original: ~z~Extreme bitches, extreme money, I always take things to the next level.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~极骚的马子，极多的钱，我总是能让东西上升到新的境界。

E2AUD.original: ~z~Money talks. Money say jump, cat say how high.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~有钱能使鬼推磨。钱说跳，手下就问多高。

E2AUD.original: ~z~When he gets out, if he ever does, it won't be the same world.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~等他出来了，如果他出的来的话，时代也已经变了。

E2AUD.original: ~z~True that, that right. I ain't no slut, jumping into any nigga give me the eye.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~确实啊，没错。我又不是荡妇，黑鬼抛个媚眼就蹦人怀里。
~z~就像Malcolm X？~n~(美国黑人民权运动家)

E2AUD.original: ~z~America is the business capital of the world 'cause that's how we roll.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~美国是世界商业之都，就是这么回事。

E2AUD.original: ~z~It's Christmas every day when you're rolling with this nigga.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~你跟这个黑鬼混的话每天都是圣诞节。

E2AUD.original: ~z~Pato! No money and a good earner is dead.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~够了！钱没赚到能赚钱的人又死了。

E2AUD.original: ~z~Come over there and you'll see what it's like rolling with the big boys.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~到那边来你就会感受到和大个子们在一起的感觉。

E2AUD.original: ~z~We're nervous. Will you oversee the deal and check everything is cool?
E2AUD.translated: ~z~我们很担心。你能帮忙盯下这次交易，确保一切顺利吗？

E2AUD.original: ~z~U.C. I know. Fucking feds is everywhere. I feel like they want me bad.
E2AUD.translated: ~z~卧底，我知道。狗日的FIB到处都是。感觉他们很想抓我。
